<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - TransTechnology started.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - TransTechnology started.</headline>
<dateline>CHICAGO 1997-06-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>EVEREN Securities Inc said Thursday it initiated coverage of TransTechnology Corp with a buy rating for both the intermediate and long terms.</p>
<p>EVEREN said it set a six-month price objective of $31 a share and an 18-month target of $35.</p>
<p>TransTechnology, which provides specialty fasteners and rescue hoist and hook products, earns above-average margins by avoiding commodity products and targeting niche markets where it can take leading market shares, EVEREN said.</p>
<p>EVEREN said it estimates fiscal 1998 earnings per share at $2.17 versus $1.92 in fiscal 1997. For fiscal 1999, EVEREN expects $2.52.</p>
<p>TransTechnology was up 1/4 at 19-7/8.</p>
<p>((--Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787))</p>
